These are Puzzles for 4x7 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x7-Level-2-1::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: 7up, coffee, fanta, juice, soy-milk, sprite, tea
7 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, cat, goldfish, fish, chinchilla, ferret, lizard
The people grow 7 different varities of flowers: daffodil, rose, zinnia, amaryllis, orchid, iris, sunflower
The people use 7 different means of transport: bike, jet-ski, quad-bike, ship, subway, train, van
 1. the person who growsamaryllis is on the far right##1
 2. the person who growsorchid is the owner of the fish##1
 3. the person driving the subway is the person who growszinnia##1
 4. the owner of the cat is on the left of the person driving the train##1
 5. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the right of the owner of the lizard##1
 6. the person drinking coffee is the person who growszinnia##1
 7. the person driving the van is on the right of the owner of the chinchilla##1
 8. the person driving the ship is between the person driving the van and the owner of the ferret##2
 9. the owner of the chinchilla is on the right of the person driving the quad-bike##1
10. the person drinking fanta is in the middle##1
11. the person who growsdaffodil is the person drinking soy-milk##1
12. the person drinking soy-milk is the person driving the bike##1
13. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the owner of the goldfish##1
14. the owner of the ferret is the person driving the quad-bike##1
15. the person driving the train is on the left of the owner of the lizard##1
16. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the person drinking sprite##1
17. the person who growsiris is on the left of the owner of the goldfish##1
18. the person drinking tea is on the right of the owner of the chinchilla##1
19. the person who growssunflower is on the right of the person driving the jet-ski##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |    3     |     4      |     5     |    6     |    7    |
| Beverage      | coffee  | sprite        | soy-milk | fanta      | juice     | 7up      | tea     |
| Pet   | cat | fish         | lizard   | guinea-pig | ferret    | chinchilla | goldfish |
| Flower         | zinnia | orchid | daffodil | rose | sunflower  | iris  | amaryllis    |
| Transport     | subway  | train         | bike     | jet-ski    | quad-bike | ship     | van     |

